                  INNER JOIN notifications ON notifications.id = user_has_notification.notification_id 
                  INNER JOIN rep ON rep.idrep = notifications.author
          WHERE user_id = '74' AND deleted = 0 
          ORDER BY timestamp DESC

		 5487 Prepare	SELECT
					rep.idrep,
					rep.user_name,
					count(rawClicks.idclicks) Clicks,
					SUM(CASE WHEN rawClicks.click_type = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) UniqueClicks,
					count(pc.id) PendingConversions,
					rep.lft,
					rep.rgt
				FROM
					rep
					
				INNER JOIN privileges p on rep.idrep = p.rep_idrep
				
				LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks ON rawClicks.rep_idrep = rep.idrep
				
				LEFT JOIN pending_conversions pc ON rawClicks.idclicks = pc.click_id  AND pc.converted = 0
				
				WHERE
					rep.referrer_repid = ? AND rawClicks.first_timestamp BETWEEN ? AND ?  and rawClicks.click_type !=2
				 
			 GROUP BY  rep.idrep
			 ORDER BY Clicks DESC
		 5487 Execute	SELECT
					rep.idrep,
					rep.user_name,
					count(rawClicks.idclicks) Clicks,
					SUM(CASE WHEN rawClicks.click_type = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) UniqueClicks,
					count(pc.id) PendingConversions,
					rep.lft,
					rep.rgt
				FROM
					rep
					
				INNER JOIN privileges p on rep.idrep = p.rep_idrep
				
				LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks ON rawClicks.rep_idrep = rep.idrep
				
				LEFT JOIN pending_conversions pc ON rawClicks.idclicks = pc.click_id  AND pc.converted = 0
				
				WHERE
					rep.referrer_repid = '74' AND rawClicks.first_timestamp BETWEEN '2019-06-22 07:00:00' AND '2019-06-23 06:59:59'  and rawClicks.click_type !=2
				 
			 GROUP BY  rep.idrep
			 ORDER BY Clicks DESC
		 5487 Close stmt	
		 5487 Prepare	SELECT
					rep.idrep,
					rep.user_name,
					count(c.id) Conversions,
					sum(c.paid) Revenue,
					count(u.id) FreeSignUps,
					sum(deducted.paid) Deductions,
					rep.lft,
					rep.rgt
				FROM
					rep
					
				INNER JOIN privileges p on rep.idrep = p.rep_idrep
				
				LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks ON rawClicks.rep_idrep = rep.idrep
				
				
				LEFT JOIN conversions c on rawClicks.idclicks = c.click_id
				
				LEFT JOIN free_sign_ups u on rawClicks.idclicks = u.click_id
				
				LEFT JOIN deductions ON deductions.conversion_id = c.id
				
				LEFT JOIN conversions deducted ON deducted.id = deductions.conversion_id
				
				
				WHERE
					c.timestamp BETWEEN ? AND ? AND rep.referrer_repid = ?
				 
			 GROUP BY  rep.idrep
			 ORDER BY Conversions DESC

		 5491 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(rawClicks.idclicks) Clicks,
                    SUM(CASE WHEN rawClicks.click_type = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) UniqueClicks,
                    count(pending_conversions.id) as PendingConversions
                FROM
                    offer
                LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                    ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                LEFT JOIN pending_conversions
                    ON pending_conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks 
                    AND pending_conversions.converted = 0
                
                WHERE rawClicks.first_timestamp BETWEEN ? AND ? 
                    AND rawClicks.click_type !=2  
                    AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = ?    
 
                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer

		 5491 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,

                    count(f.id) FreeSignUps,
                    count(conversions.id) Conversions,
                    sum(conversions.paid) Revenue,
                    sum(deducted.paid) Deductions
                FROM
                    offer
                    
                    LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                        ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = ?
                    LEFT JOIN conversions 
                        ON conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN free_sign_ups f 
                        ON f.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN deductions 
                        ON deductions.conversion_id = conversions.id
                    LEFT JOIN conversions deducted 
                        ON deducted.id = deductions.conversion_id
                WHERE conversions.timestamp BETWEEN ? AND ? 
                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer

                    offer.idoffer,

                    offer

                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = '1192'

		 5487 Execute	SELECT
					rep.idrep,
					rep.user_name,
					count(c.id) Conversions,
					sum(c.paid) Revenue,
					count(u.id) FreeSignUps,
					sum(deducted.paid) Deductions,
					rep.lft,
					rep.rgt
				FROM
					rep
					
				INNER JOIN privileges p on rep.idrep = p.rep_idrep
				
				LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks ON rawClicks.rep_idrep = rep.idrep
				
				
				LEFT JOIN conversions c on rawClicks.idclicks = c.click_id
				
				LEFT JOIN free_sign_ups u on rawClicks.idclicks = u.click_id
				
				LEFT JOIN deductions ON deductions.conversion_id = c.id
				
				LEFT JOIN conversions deducted ON deducted.id = deductions.conversion_id
				
				
				WHERE
					c.timestamp BETWEEN '2019-06-22 07:00:00' AND '2019-06-23 06:59:59' AND rep.referrer_repid = '74'
				 
			 GROUP BY  rep.idrep
			 ORDER BY Conversions DESC

		 5522 Prepare	SELECT
					offer.idoffer,

					count(conversions.id) Conversions,
					sum(conversions.paid) Revenue,
					sum(deducted.paid) Deductions
				FROM
					offer
					
				LEFT JOIN rep ON rep.referrer_repid = ?
				
			
				LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = rep.idrep

		 5571 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(rawClicks.idclicks) Clicks,
                    SUM(CASE WHEN rawClicks.click_type = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) UniqueClicks,
                    count(pending_conversions.id) as PendingConversions
                FROM
                    offer

                    ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer

                    ON pending_conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks 
                    AND pending_conversions.converted = 0

                    offer.idoffer,

                    count(pending_conversions.id) as PendingConversions
                FROM
                    offer

                    ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer

                    ON pending_conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks 
                    AND pending_conversions.converted = 0

		 5571 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(f.id) FreeSignUps,
                    count(conversions.id) Conversions,
                    sum(conversions.paid) Revenue,
                    sum(deducted.paid) Deductions
                FROM
                    offer
                    
                    LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                        ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = ?
                    LEFT JOIN conversions 
                        ON conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN free_sign_ups f 
                        ON f.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN deductions 
                        ON deductions.conversion_id = conversions.id
                    LEFT JOIN conversions deducted 
                        ON deducted.id = deductions.conversion_id
                WHERE conversions.timestamp BETWEEN ? AND ? 
                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer

                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = '1300'
                    LEFT JOIN conversions 
                        ON conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks

		 5741 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,

                    offer.idoffer,

                    count(f.id) FreeSignUps,
                    count(conversions.id) Conversions,
                    sum(conversions.paid) Revenue,
                    sum(deducted.paid) Deductions
                FROM
                    offer
                    
                    LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                        ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = ?
                    LEFT JOIN conversions 
                        ON conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN free_sign_ups f 
                        ON f.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN deductions 
                        ON deductions.conversion_id = conversions.id
                    LEFT JOIN conversions deducted 
                        ON deducted.id = deductions.conversion_id
                WHERE conversions.timestamp BETWEEN ? AND ? 
                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer

		 5782 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(rawClicks.idclicks) Clicks,
                    SUM(CASE WHEN rawClicks.click_type = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) UniqueClicks,
                    count(pending_conversions.id) as PendingConversions
                FROM
                    offer
                LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                    ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                LEFT JOIN pending_conversions
                    ON pending_conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks 
                    AND pending_conversions.converted = 0
                
                WHERE rawClicks.first_timestamp BETWEEN ? AND ?

                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer

                    offer.idoffer,

                    count(pending_conversions.id) as PendingConversions
                FROM
                    offer
                LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                    ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                LEFT JOIN pending_conversions
                    ON pending_conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks 
                    AND pending_conversions.converted = 0

		 5782 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(f.id) FreeSignUps,
                    count(conversions.id) Conversions,
                    sum(conversions.paid) Revenue,
                    sum(deducted.paid) Deductions
                FROM
                    offer
                    
                    LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                        ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = ?
                    LEFT JOIN conversions 
                        ON conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN free_sign_ups f 
                        ON f.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN deductions 
                        ON deductions.conversion_id = conversions.id
                    LEFT JOIN conversions deducted 
                        ON deducted.id = deductions.conversion_id
                WHERE conversions.timestamp BETWEEN ? AND ? 
                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer
		 5782 Execute	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,

                    sum(conversions.paid) Revenue,
                    sum(deducted.paid) Deductions
                FROM
                    offer
                    
                    LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                        ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = '1192'
                    LEFT JOIN conversions 
                        ON conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN free_sign_ups f 
                        ON f.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN deductions 
                        ON deductions.conversion_id = conversions.id
                    LEFT JOIN conversions deducted 
                        ON deducted.id = deductions.conversion_id
                WHERE conversions.timestamp BETWEEN '2019-06-01 07:00:00' AND '2019-06-25 06:59:59'

		 5788 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,

                    count(rawClicks.idclicks) Clicks,

                    count(pending_conversions.id) as PendingConversions
                FROM
                    offer

                    ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer

                    ON pending_conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks

		 5788 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(f.id) FreeSignUps,
                    count(conversions.id) Conversions,
                    sum(conversions.paid) Revenue,
                    sum(deducted.paid) Deductions
                FROM
                    offer
                    
                    LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                        ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = ?
                    LEFT JOIN conversions 
                        ON conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN free_sign_ups f 
                        ON f.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN deductions 
                        ON deductions.conversion_id = conversions.id
                    LEFT JOIN conversions deducted 
                        ON deducted.id = deductions.conversion_id

                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer
		 5788 Execute	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,

                    sum(deducted.paid) Deductions
                FROM
                    offer
                    
                    LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                        ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = '1299'
                    LEFT JOIN conversions 
                        ON conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks

                        ON deductions.conversion_id = conversions.id

                    offer.idoffer,

                    count(pending_conversions.id) as PendingConversions
                FROM
                    offer

                    ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer

                    ON pending_conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks 
                    AND pending_conversions.converted = 0

		 6235 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(rawClicks.idclicks) Clicks,
                    SUM(CASE WHEN rawClicks.click_type = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) UniqueClicks,
                    count(pending_conversions.id) as PendingConversions
                FROM
                    offer
                LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                    ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                LEFT JOIN pending_conversions
                    ON pending_conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks 
                    AND pending_conversions.converted = 0
                
                WHERE rawClicks.first_timestamp BETWEEN ? AND ? 
                    AND rawClicks.click_type !=2  
                    AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = ?    
 
                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer
		 6235 Execute	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(rawClicks.idclicks) Clicks,
                    SUM(CASE WHEN rawClicks.click_type = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) UniqueClicks,
                    count(pending_conversions.id) as PendingConversions
                FROM
                    offer
                LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                    ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                LEFT JOIN pending_conversions
                    ON pending_conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks 
                    AND pending_conversions.converted = 0
                
                WHERE rawClicks.first_timestamp BETWEEN '2019-06-22 07:00:00' AND '2019-06-23 06:59:59'

		 6235 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(f.id) FreeSignUps,
                    count(conversions.id) Conversions,
                    sum(conversions.paid) Revenue,
                    sum(deducted.paid) Deductions
                FROM
                    offer
                    
                    LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                        ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = ?
                    LEFT JOIN conversions 
                        ON conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN free_sign_ups f 
                        ON f.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN deductions 
                        ON deductions.conversion_id = conversions.id
                    LEFT JOIN conversions deducted 
                        ON deducted.id = deductions.conversion_id
                WHERE conversions.timestamp BETWEEN ? AND ? 
                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer
		 6235 Execute	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,

                    sum(conversions.paid) Revenue,
                    sum(deducted.paid) Deductions
                FROM
                    offer
                    
                    LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                        ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = '1084'
                    LEFT JOIN conversions 
                        ON conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN free_sign_ups f 
                        ON f.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks

                        ON deductions.conversion_id = conversions.id
                    LEFT JOIN conversions deducted

                WHERE conversions.timestamp BETWEEN '2019-06-22 07:00:00' AND '2019-06-23 06:59:59' 
                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer

					rep.idrep,
					rep.user_name,
					count(rawClicks.idclicks) Clicks,
					SUM(CASE WHEN rawClicks.click_type = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) UniqueClicks,
					count(pc.id) PendingConversions,
					rep.lft,
					rep.rgt
				FROM
					rep
					
				INNER JOIN privileges p on rep.idrep = p.rep_idrep
				
				LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks ON rawClicks.rep_idrep = rep.idrep

		 6392 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,

                    count(rawClicks.idclicks) Clicks,

                    count(pending_conversions.id) as PendingConversions
                FROM
                    offer

                    ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                LEFT JOIN pending_conversions
                    ON pending_conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks 
                    AND pending_conversions.converted = 0

                    offer.idoffer,

                    sum(deducted.paid) Deductions
                FROM
                    offer
                    
                    LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                        ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = ?
                    LEFT JOIN conversions 
                        ON conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN free_sign_ups f 
                        ON f.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN deductions 
                        ON deductions.conversion_id = conversions.id

                        ON deducted.id = deductions.conversion_id
                WHERE conversions.timestamp BETWEEN ? AND ?

                  INNER JOIN notifications ON notifications.id = user_has_notification.notification_id 
                  INNER JOIN rep ON rep.idrep = notifications.author
          WHERE user_id = '1296' AND deleted = 0 
          ORDER BY timestamp DESC

		 7067 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(rawClicks.idclicks) Clicks,
                    SUM(CASE WHEN rawClicks.click_type = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) UniqueClicks,
                    count(pending_conversions.id) as PendingConversions
                FROM
                    offer
                LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                    ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                LEFT JOIN pending_conversions
                    ON pending_conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks 
                    AND pending_conversions.converted = 0
                
                WHERE rawClicks.first_timestamp BETWEEN ? AND ? 
                    AND rawClicks.click_type !=2  
                    AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = ?    
 
                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer
		 7067 Execute	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(rawClicks.idclicks) Clicks,
                    SUM(CASE WHEN rawClicks.click_type = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) UniqueClicks,
                    count(pending_conversions.id) as PendingConversions
                FROM
                    offer
                LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                    ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                LEFT JOIN pending_conversions
                    ON pending_conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks 
                    AND pending_conversions.converted = 0
                
                WHERE rawClicks.first_timestamp BETWEEN '2019-06-22 07:00:00' AND '2019-06-24 06:59:59' 
                    AND rawClicks.click_type !=2  
                    AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = '1300'    
 
                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer
		 7067 Close stmt	
		 7067 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(f.id) FreeSignUps,
                    count(conversions.id) Conversions,
                    sum(conversions.paid) Revenue,
                    sum(deducted.paid) Deductions
                FROM
                    offer
                    
                    LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                        ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = ?
                    LEFT JOIN conversions 
                        ON conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN free_sign_ups f 
                        ON f.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN deductions 
                        ON deductions.conversion_id = conversions.id
                    LEFT JOIN conversions deducted 
                        ON deducted.id = deductions.conversion_id
                WHERE conversions.timestamp BETWEEN ? AND ? 
                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer
		 7067 Execute	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(f.id) FreeSignUps,
                    count(conversions.id) Conversions,
                    sum(conversions.paid) Revenue,
                    sum(deducted.paid) Deductions
                FROM
                    offer
                    
                    LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                        ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = '1300'
                    LEFT JOIN conversions 
                        ON conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN free_sign_ups f 
                        ON f.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN deductions 
                        ON deductions.conversion_id = conversions.id
                    LEFT JOIN conversions deducted 
                        ON deducted.id = deductions.conversion_id
                WHERE conversions.timestamp BETWEEN '2019-06-22 07:00:00' AND '2019-06-24 06:59:59' 
                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer
		 7067 Close stmt

		 7088 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(rawClicks.idclicks) Clicks,
                    SUM(CASE WHEN rawClicks.click_type = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) UniqueClicks,
                    count(pending_conversions.id) as PendingConversions
                FROM
                    offer
                LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                    ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer

                    ON pending_conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks 
                    AND pending_conversions.converted = 0

		 7088 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(f.id) FreeSignUps,
                    count(conversions.id) Conversions,
                    sum(conversions.paid) Revenue,
                    sum(deducted.paid) Deductions
                FROM
                    offer
                    
                    LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                        ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = ?
                    LEFT JOIN conversions 
                        ON conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN free_sign_ups f 
                        ON f.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN deductions 
                        ON deductions.conversion_id = conversions.id
                    LEFT JOIN conversions deducted 
                        ON deducted.id = deductions.conversion_id
                WHERE conversions.timestamp BETWEEN ? AND ? 
                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer

                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = '1300'

		 7214 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(rawClicks.idclicks) Clicks,
                    SUM(CASE WHEN rawClicks.click_type = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) UniqueClicks,
                    count(pending_conversions.id) as PendingConversions
                FROM
                    offer
                LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                    ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                LEFT JOIN pending_conversions
                    ON pending_conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks 
                    AND pending_conversions.converted = 0
                
                WHERE rawClicks.first_timestamp BETWEEN ? AND ? 
                    AND rawClicks.click_type !=2  
                    AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = ?    
 
                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer
		 7214 Execute	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(rawClicks.idclicks) Clicks,
                    SUM(CASE WHEN rawClicks.click_type = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) UniqueClicks,
                    count(pending_conversions.id) as PendingConversions
                FROM
                    offer
                LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                    ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                LEFT JOIN pending_conversions
                    ON pending_conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks 
                    AND pending_conversions.converted = 0
                
                WHERE rawClicks.first_timestamp BETWEEN '2019-06-22 07:00:00' AND '2019-06-23 06:59:59' 
                    AND rawClicks.click_type !=2  
                    AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = '1300'    
 
                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer
		 7214 Close stmt	
		 7214 Prepare	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(f.id) FreeSignUps,
                    count(conversions.id) Conversions,
                    sum(conversions.paid) Revenue,
                    sum(deducted.paid) Deductions
                FROM
                    offer
                    
                    LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                        ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = ?
                    LEFT JOIN conversions 
                        ON conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN free_sign_ups f 
                        ON f.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN deductions 
                        ON deductions.conversion_id = conversions.id
                    LEFT JOIN conversions deducted 
                        ON deducted.id = deductions.conversion_id
                WHERE conversions.timestamp BETWEEN ? AND ? 
                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer
		 7214 Execute	SELECT
                    offer.idoffer,
                    offer.offer_name,
                    count(f.id) FreeSignUps,
                    count(conversions.id) Conversions,
                    sum(conversions.paid) Revenue,
                    sum(deducted.paid) Deductions
                FROM
                    offer
                    
                    LEFT JOIN clicks rawClicks 
                        ON rawClicks.offer_idoffer = offer.idoffer 
                        AND rawClicks.rep_idrep = '1300'
                    LEFT JOIN conversions 
                        ON conversions.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN free_sign_ups f 
                        ON f.click_id = rawClicks.idclicks
                    LEFT JOIN deductions 
                        ON deductions.conversion_id = conversions.id
                    LEFT JOIN conversions deducted 
                        ON deducted.id = deductions.conversion_id
                WHERE conversions.timestamp BETWEEN '2019-06-22 07:00:00' AND '2019-06-23 06:59:59' 
                GROUP BY offer.idoffer, rawClicks.offer_idoffer
		 7214 Close stmt
